com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.bridge
Interface ModelExtractor<T>

Type Parameters:
T - The models' type of the Rhizosphere visualization this extractor is attached to.
All Known Implementing Classes:
JavaScriptObjectModelBridge, JSONObjectModelBridge, JSONStringModelBridge, ModelBridge
public interface ModelExtractor<T>

Extracts the Java object that was originally used to represent a Rhizosphere model (via Rhizosphere.addModel(Object)) from the JavaScriptObject (used in the visualization javascript library code) that wraps it.

Author:
battlehorse@google.com (Riccardo Govoni)
